  "text": "Overweight and obesity were categorized according to the age-and sex-specific percentiles for BMI of national reference standards [CITATION_1] . Overweight was defined as BMI $ 85th percentile and ,95th percentile, and obesity was defined as BMI $ 95th percentile.",
